  <card id="bofer" title="Delhi High Court quashes bribery charges in Bofors case"> 
        <p>
      &nbsp;&nbsp;The Delhi High Court today quashed the charges under the 
Prevention of Courruption Act against teh three Hinduja brothers in the 
Bofor case.<br/> <br/>It held that there was no evidence to support the 
allegation that the brothers bribed the late Prime Minister, Rajiv Gandhi, and 
the then Defence Secretary, S.K.Bhatnagar, for winning the Bofors howitzer contract.<br/>

    </p> 
