  <card id="pota" title="POTA panel has right to call for records:court"> 

       <p>&nbsp;&nbsp;The Madras High Court today ruled that the Central 
Review Committee under the Prevention of Terrorism Act had been validly constituted; that it 
rightly called for records from the Tamil Nadu Government in some pending POTA
cases and that it could address the state government if it concluded that the 
cases were fit to be withdrawn
